Name: bpl
Version: 0.0.1
Summary: Simple Bayesian models for football leagues
Home-page: https://github.com/anguswilliams91/FPL
Author: Angus Williams <anguswilliams91@gmail.com>
Author-email: anguswilliams91@gmail.com
